title: Call Of Duty Modern Warfare 3 (MW3) and Teckno Gods
description:
Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 (stylized as Call of Duty: MW3) is a first-person shooter video game, developed by Infinity Ward and Sledgehammer Games, with assistance from Raven Software, and published by Activision. ... The game's campaign follows Modern Warfare 2 and begins right after the events of its final mission.


THIS IS NOT A REPACK OR ANYTHING OF THE SORT. THIS IS A PRE-INSTALLED VERSION OF THE GAME ALONG WITH TECKNO GODS MOD FOR MULTIPLAYER

Spec	                   Requirement
Free Disk Space	           16 GB of Free Disk Space
Video Card	           NVIDIA GeForce 8600GT or ATI Radeon X1950 or better
Misc Video Card/Memory	   Support for Shader 3.0 or later and 256 MB of Video RAM
Sound Card	           DirectX Compatible Sound Card
RAM                        4GB
